# 📊 Power BI Data Analytics Projects

This repository contains **Power BI projects focused on data analytics and business intelligence**.

The dashboards analyze large datasets related to the **data job market**, transforming raw data into interactive visualizations and actionable insights.

Each project includes its own **detailed README** explaining:

- dataset information
- business questions
- data modeling
- DAX calculations
- dashboard features

For more details, please refer to the **README** inside each project folder.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies

These projects were developed using:

- 📊 Power BI
- 🧮 DAX
- 🔄 Power Query
- 🗄️ Data Modeling
- 📈 Data Visualization

---

## 📁 Projects Included

### 🌎 Global Data Jobs Analytics Dashboard

Interactive dashboard analyzing the **global data job market**.

Features include:

- **drill-through** analysis by job title
- global job distribution **map**
- **salary** statistics
- **job platform** analysis
- **work modality** insights

📂 See project folder for full details.

---

### 🇦🇷 Argentina Data Jobs Dashboard

Power BI dashboard focused on the **data job market in Argentina**.

Key analysis includes:

- **most demanded** technical skills
- **salary insights** for data-related roles
- dynamic **filtering** by job title
- interactive visualizations using **field parameters**

📂 See project folder for full details.

---

## 📊 Purpose of This Repository

The purpose of this repository is to showcase **Power BI dashboards and data analytics workflows**, including:

- transforming large datasets
- building interactive dashboards
- performing data modeling
- creating analytical metrics with DAX

Each project demonstrates different **analytical techniques and Power BI features** used in real-world data analysis scenarios.

